  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244945.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>一名微软发言人在今天证实了Xbox One可以通过Xbox Live边下载边玩游戏(stream games)，对于那些愿意购买了数字版游戏就想立即开始玩的人们来说，这绝对是个好事情。</strong>最近被证实的是，Xbox One可以在从光盘安装到硬盘的时候玩游戏；而今天，微软证实了数字下载版拥有了相同的能力。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec170e1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244945.htm&amp;t=%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%AF%81%E5%AE%9EXbox+One%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BE%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E8%BE%B9%E7%8E%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244945.htm&amp;t=%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%AF%81%E5%AE%9EXbox+One%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BE%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E8%BE%B9%E7%8E%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244945.htm&amp;t=%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%AF%81%E5%AE%9EXbox+One%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BE%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E8%BE%B9%E7%8E%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244945.htm&amp;t=%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%AF%81%E5%AE%9EXbox+One%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BE%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E8%BE%B9%E7%8E%A9%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email