  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244944.htm", 
  "description": "<p>如果有人对美国国家安全局（NSA）仍在继续的窥探行为感到恼火，他将会是美国商务部，而不是提倡保护隐私权的人。<strong>最近的一些事实对对美国国家安全来说没有什么威胁，反倒是对美国经济造成了威胁。而作为微软，实在应该一刻不停地召开会议来讨论如何处理接下来会发生的事。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec170e0/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244944.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D+%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244944.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D+%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244944.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D+%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244944.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D+%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww