  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244943.htm", 
  "description": "<p>对于有些人来说天生就是绘画的天才，不过随着科学技术的发展计算设备能够部分替代手工进行绘画。<strong>最近在Kickstarter平台上年轻的发明家Sylvia Todd开始为自己的WaterColorBot的手工绘画机器人募集资金，除了能够绘画一些简单的矢量图形之外还能模仿人的操作进行绘画。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec170de/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244943.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%B6Todd%E4%B8%BA%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E7%BB%98%E7%94%BB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8WaterColorBot%E5%8B%9F%E9%9B%86%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244943.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%B6Todd%E4%B8%BA%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E7%BB%98%E7%94%BB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8WaterColorBot%E5%8B%9F%E9%9B%86%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244943.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%B6Todd%E4%B8%BA%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E7%BB%98%E7%94%BB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8WaterColorBot%E5%8B%9F%E9%9B%86%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244943.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E5%AE%B6Todd%E4%B8%BA%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E7%BB%98%E7%94%BB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8WaterColorBot%E5%8B%9F%E9%9B%86%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/s