  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244941.htm", 
  "description": "<p>尽管微软才刚刚正式发布Windows 8.1，但关于其下一代完全版本升级的操作系统Windows9的消息就已经在网络中各种流传了。<strong>看起来似乎微软企图利用Windows 9统一现有的两大移动应用平台，所以未来平板和手机将有可能运行同一款操作系统。</strong>据一篇来自UnwiredView.Com的报道称，微软近来宣布的重组计划就是为了在明年能够实现平板和手机统一操作系统所迈出的重要一步。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec170db/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244941.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0Windows+9%E5%B0%86%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83Metro%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%92%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244941.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0Windows+9%E5%B0%86%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83Metro%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%92%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244941.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0Windows+9%E5%B0%86%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83Metro%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%92%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244941.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0Windows+9%E5%B0%86%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83Metro%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%92%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F